# User Stories

## User Model
- As a user, I should be able to register
- As a user, I should be able to login

## User Profile Model
- As a user, I should be able to read my profile
- As a user, I should be able to update my profile
- As a user, I should be able to delete my profile

## Application Model
- As a user, I should be able to create an application
- As a user, I should be able to read an application
- As a user, I should be able to update an application
- As a user, I should be able to delete an application

## Requirement Model
- As a user, I should be able to create a requirement
- As a user, I should be able to read a requirement
- As a user, I should be able to update a requirement
- As a user, I should be able to delete a requirement

